compute_fit_mx_plus_b <- function(data, scales, slope = 0, intercept = NULL){
  
  intercept <- intercept %||% mean(data$y)
  
  data |>
    dplyr::mutate(yend = y,
                  y = slope * .data$x + intercept) |> 
    dplyr::mutate(xend = .data$x)
    
  
}
